msgstr "`utf8`"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:18
msgid "Host-facing built-in modules such as `io`, `os`, and `package` are intentionally not available. Use `ptool` APIs such as `ptool.fs`, `ptool.os`, `ptool.path`, and `ptool.run` for filesystem, environment, process, network, and other runtime operations instead."
msgstr "像 `io`、`os`、`package` 这类面向宿主环境的内建模块会被有意禁用。 文件系统、环境变量、进程、网络等运行时操作应改用 `ptool.fs`、 `ptool.os`、`ptool.path`、`ptool.run` 等 API。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:23
msgid "If you want to pass arguments to a Lua script, you can do it like this:"
msgstr "如果你想向 Lua 脚本传参，可以这样做："

