msgid "Shebang is supported, so you can add this to the top of the file:"
msgstr "也支持 shebang，因此你可以把下面这行放到文件开头："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:46
msgid "ptool.use"
msgstr "ptool.use"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:48
msgid "`v0.1.0` - Introduced. `v0.7.0` - Added Cargo-style version requirement expressions."
msgstr "`v0.1.0` - 引入。 `v0.7.0` - 新增 Cargo 风格版本要求表达式支持。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:51
msgid "`ptool.use` declares the required `ptool` version or version requirement for a script."
msgstr "`ptool.use` 用来声明脚本要求的 `ptool` 版本或版本要求。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:60
msgid "The argument accepts either a plain semantic version string or a Cargo-style version requirement expression."
msgstr "参数既可以是普通的语义化版本字符串，也可以是 Cargo 风格的版本要求表达式。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:62
msgid "A plain version string supports an optional `v` prefix, such as `v0.1.0` or `0.1.0`, and keeps the historical behavior of declaring the minimum required `ptool` version."
msgstr "普通版本字符串可选带 `v` 前缀，例如 `v0.1.0` 或 `0.1.0`，并保持历史行为，即声明最低要求的 `ptool` 版本。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:65
msgid "Requirement expressions support operators and patterns such as `^0.6.0`, `~0.6.0`, `>=0.6.0, <0.7.0`, `1.*`, and `1.2.*`."
msgstr "版本要求表达式支持 `^0.6.0`、`~0.6.0`、`>=0.6.0, <0.7.0`、`1.*` 和 `1.2.*` 等运算符和模式。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:67
msgid "Requirement expressions also accept version components with an optional `v` prefix, such as `>= v0.6.0, < 0.7.0`."
msgstr "版本要求表达式里的版本组件也支持可选的 `v` 前缀，例如 `>= v0.6.0, < 0.7.0`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:69
msgid "If the current `ptool` version does not satisfy the declared version or requirement, the script exits immediately with an error."
msgstr "如果当前 `ptool` 版本不满足声明的版本或版本要求，脚本会立即退出并报错。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:72
msgid "ptool.version"
msgstr "ptool.version"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:74
msgid "`v0.8.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.8.0` - 引入。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:76
msgid "`ptool.version()` returns the current `ptool` version string."
msgstr "`ptool.version()` 会返回当前 `ptool` 的版本字符串。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:78
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:78"
msgid "Returns: `string`."
msgstr "返回：`string`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:79
msgid "The returned value is a semantic version string such as `0.7.2`."
msgstr "返回值是一个语义化版本字符串，例如 `0.7.2`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:80
msgid "Use this when a script needs to print, record, or compare the runtime `ptool` version."
msgstr "当脚本需要打印、记录或比较运行时 `ptool` 版本时，可以使用它。"

