msgid "Currently supported fields:"
msgstr "当前支持的字段："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:357
msgid "`run` (table, optional): Default configuration for `ptool.run`, `ptool.run_capture`, `ptool.pipe`, and `ptool.run_shell`. Supported fields:"
