msgstr "`echo`（boolean，可选）：默认是否回显。默认值为 `true`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:357
msgid "`check` (boolean, optional): Whether failures raise an error by default. Defaults to `false`."
